This is a Web Application for Asthmatic patients to manage their medication patterns which aid in better treatment.

Framework - Django (python)
Storage - Mysql 

Set your path in settings.py 
*STATIC_ROOT = path + '/static/'
*TEMPLATE_DIRS = ( path+'/mytemplates/')

Fill up the SendGrid API credentials in settings.py 

EMAIL_HOST_USER = 'username'
EMAIL_HOST_PASSWORD = 'password'


After setting up the environment and seeing up the path 

1) inside SAM folder run - python manage.py syncdb
2) To start the server - python manage.py run server

The app will now be available at in http://localhost:3000/ 
